比賽的媒體採訪會進行地相當順利，而有些報導稱這場比賽「令人毛骨悚然」<ref name=crashnet>{{cite web|title=F1 British Grand Prix: Hamilton beats Williams, rain in British GP thriller|url=http://www.crash.net/f1/race-report/220809/1/hamilton-beats-williams-rain-in-british-gp-thriller.html|website=crash.net|accessdate=2015-07-05|date=2015-07-05|archive-date=2015-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707004004/http://www.crash.net/f1/race-report/220809/1/hamilton-beats-williams-rain-in-british-gp-thriller.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>且能「為這項備受抨擊的運動注入新血」。<ref name="guardpostrace">{{cite web|last1=Weaver|first1=Paul|title=Lewis Hamilton wins British F1 GP from Nico Rosberg at damp Silverstone|url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/jul/05/lewis-hamilton-wins-british-f1-gp-nico-rosberg|publisher=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-07-05|date=2015-07-05|archive-date=2015-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151009032922/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2015/jul/05/lewis-hamilton-wins-british-f1-gp-nico-rosberg|dead-url=no}}</ref>特別是漢米爾頓的表現被視為相當傑出。<ref name=bbcpostrace>{{cite web|last1=Benson|first1=Andrew|title=Lewis Hamilton wins British GP brilliantly after late rain|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/33401990|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2015-07-05|date=2015-07-05|archive-date=2015-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706222727/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/33401990|dead-url=no}}</ref>這位世界冠軍坦言梅賽德斯在起跑時失去了他們的位置，也為粉絲增加比賽的可看度，並接著說：「你無法想像我有多麼開心。我在最後一圈時更流下了眼淚。」<ref name=bbcpostrace />

經過前幾圈與隊友馬薩爭奪領先地位後，維爾特利·鮑達斯表示他確信他能拉開與後方梅賽德斯的差距。不過，他堅稱「沒有人應該被限制。這樣就不是賽車，但當時我確實有不錯的機會來超車」。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Barretto|first1=Lawrence|title=British Grand Prix: Bottas 'would have been able to pull a gap'|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/119864|website=autosport.com|accessdate=2015-07-05|date=2015-07-05|archive-date=2015-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706071138/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/119864|dead-url=no}}</ref>紅牛車隊主席[[克里斯蒂安·霍納|克里斯蒂安·霍納]]在賽後宣稱，一次在濕滑賽道上的打滑浪費了丹尼爾·科維亞特爭奪頒獎台名次的機會。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Barretto|first1=Lawrence|title=British GP spin cost Daniil Kvyat chance to fight for F1 podium|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/119863|website=autosport.com|accessdate=2015-07-05|date=2015-07-05|archive-date=2015-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706070013/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/119863|dead-url=no}}</ref>賽後，賽會決定不對在第一圈引發事故的蓮花與麥拉倫車手採取任何行動。<ref>{{cite web|title=No penalties for opening-lap collisions|url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/7/no-further-action-over-opening-lap-carnage.html|publisher=FIA|accessdate=2015-07-05|date=2015-07-05|archive-date=2015-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150706200707/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/7/no-further-action-over-opening-lap-carnage.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
[[File:Alonso_Britain_2015.jpg|thumb]]取得他本季的第一個積分。]]
這場勝利讓漢米爾頓在車手積分榜上將與羅斯堡的差距擴大至17分。<ref name=bbcpostrace />梅賽德斯靠著連續九站讓兩位車手皆站上頒獎台，打破了法拉利在{{le|1952年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1952 Formula One season|1952}}至{{le|1953年世界一級方程式錦標賽|1953 Formula One season|1953年}}間所寫下的紀錄。當時法拉利達成連續八場有至少兩位車手站上頒獎台，雖然往往會有多於兩位的車手上場比賽。<ref name=spox/>

比賽結束後隔天，一場關於據稱梅賽德斯讓其技工在第14圈時到維修道準備卻沒有執行進站，而違反規則的小風波在媒體間浮現。[[蘇茜·沃爾夫|蘇茜·沃爾夫]]隨後公布她傳給身為梅賽德斯車隊老闆的丈夫{{le|托托·沃爾夫|Toto Wolff}}的文字訊息，稱這起事件是「一場小遊戲」，未能讓威廉斯車隊提前把他們的車輛叫進維修站中。儘管如此，賽會也未對此作出處分。<ref>{{cite web|title=British GP: Mercedes' fake pit stop: breaking the rules or fun tactic?|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/33403578|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2015-07-07|date=2015-07-05|archive-date=2015-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150707171032/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/formula1/33403578|dead-url=no}}</ref>

